<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1426695-on-a-scale-of-rachel-maddow-s-biography-to">On a scale of Rachel Maddow&#39;s biography to The Turner Diaries: How &#39;racist&#39; is this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1426695'><a id="like_count_community_question_1426695" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1426695?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F95105.Oldest_Living_Confederate_Widow_Tells_All">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1426695-on-a-scale-of-rachel-maddow-s-biography-to">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1426695-on-a-scale-of-rachel-maddow-s-biography-to">Add your answer</a>
</li>
