            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Beware of using up your last forty years in being the curator of your first fifty.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/948993-beware-of-using-up-your-last-forty-years-in-being">6 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
